data.description: Welcome to comfort and affordability at 889 E. Lehman Street in Lebanon Pa.  This inviting home, situated on a prime, nearly half-acre fenced in corner lot, featuring 2,276 square feet of living space, with 2.5 baths, and potential 5 bedrooms. This home is a testament to spacious and efficient living, featuring economical gas heating and a detached garage for added convenience. You’re going to love the covered front porch for relaxing evenings and the overall charm this home boasts.  Enter to a very large living room with original hardwood flooring, high ceilings with brick fireplace.  Follow to the sunlit sunroom offering gorgeous views of the expansive yard, creating a peaceful retreat.  The dining room is a fantastic space for large gatherings adorn with gorgeous lighting.  Entertainment is made easy with the adjacent kitchen and rear yard access and laundry area.  There is also a convenient half bath on the main level.   The second level features three bedrooms.  A large primary bedroom with lots of natural lighting  and an incredible full bath with gorgeous tile.  There are two other nicely sized bedrooms on the second level, one with a pass through.  This second level also features a remodeled full hall bath making that 2 full baths and one half bath overall. The third floor offers additional flexible space, featuring two private rooms, ideal for a home office, or bedrooms four and five. Located close to shopping and major roadways, with an easy commute to Berks and Lancaster Counties, this home combines the appeal of a large living area with the practicality of modern amenities, making it an ideal choice for those seeking value and space. This home is ready to be yours, where comfort meets convenience in a beautifully appointed setting.
